data.description: 3 bedroom 2 bath ranch-style home located on a quiet street in Barrington Park. Built in 2003 this brick and vinyl home features over 1300 sq.ft. of living area, with updated landscaping, a huge fenced backyard.  Inside is a completely open living and kitchen area with separate island.  Laundry closet, and corner fireplace as well. All three bedrooms are together with tub/shower units in both. The entire home is wood laminate or tile flooring. There is a great backyard with full privacy fencing, a large shed, and patio with fire pit as well. Easy access to Battlefield to the north and Republic Road to the south. Jeffries, Carver, Parkview Schools.
